org.timepedia.chronoscope.client.render
Interface Panel

All Known Implementing Classes:
AbstractPanel, AxisPanel, CompositeAxisPanel, DatasetLegendPanel, DateRangePanel, DomainAxisPanel, LegendAxisPanel, OverviewAxisPanel, RangeAxisPanel, RangePanel, ZoomPanel
public interface Panel

Basic representation of a UI panel that has a size and screen position.

Author:
Chad Takahashi
